                <h3>Course Records</h3>
                <p>Squaw Creek’s course record prior to 2016 renovation is jointly held by 7 players:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Gene Doelling - July 1980</li>
                    <li>Tommy Fincher - August 1981</li>
                    <li>Bobby Golightly - August 1986</li>
                    <li>Jeev Singh - May 1997</li>
                    <li>Jaxon Bringman - April 1999</li>
                    <li>Andy Hobson - April 2004</li>
                    <li>Dean Hayhurst - May 2012</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Squaw Creek course record after 2016 renovation has yet to be established. Come out and take your shot at history!</p>
